title: Omelette's | Life Saving Leftovers
description:
The complete guide to Omelette. Learn to make it perfectly, and inspire yourself with 3 stunning fast and delicious examples.

This video is part of a new series : Life Saving Leftovers. A waterfall of tips to make you a better cook with whatever there's in the fridge. Yes you can !
